trans-unit.source: Defines an abstract base class for composable part definitions, which describe and enable the creation of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 설명 하 고 만들 수 있는 구성 가능한 부분 정의 대 한 추상 기본 클래스를 정의 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> class.
Creates a new instance of a part that the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: 파트의 새 인스턴스를 만듭니다는 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> 에 대해 설명 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Derived types that override this method should return a new instance of a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object every time that the method is invoked and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 재정의 하는 파생된 형식에서의 새 인스턴스를 반환 해야는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>개체 메서드가 호출 되 고 반환 해서는 안 될 때마다 `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the objects exported by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 가져옵니다 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> 이 정의 파트에서 내보낸 개체를 설명 하는 개체 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성의 재정의 반환할 수 없습니다 `null`합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not provide exported objects, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>가 만든 개체는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>내보낸된 개체를 제공, 빈 반환 하지 않는 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>컬렉션 대신.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the exported objects provided by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> 에서 제공 하는 내보낸된 개체를 설명 하는 개체 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> 가 만든 개체는 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성의 재정의 반환할 수 없습니다 `null`합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the metadata for this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 이 대 한 메타 데이터의 컬렉션을 가져옵니다 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성의 재정의 읽기 전용 반환 해야 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>와 같은 개체를 대/소문자 구분, 비 언어적 비교자와 함께 <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>를 반환할 수 없습니다 및 `null`.</xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object instead.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>빈 반환, 메타 데이터를 포함 하지 않습니다 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>개체를 대신 합니다.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the metadata for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 메타 데이터를 포함 하는 컬렉션의 <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object.
trans-unit.target: 기본값은 비어 있거나, 읽기 전용 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> 개체입니다.
